lead_paragraph: Renault announced the Formula One comeback of Danish driver Kevin Magnussen at the launch on Wednesday of a new-look team that will put the French carmaker back on the starting grid as a constructor.

headline.print_headline: Magnussen Returns in New-Look Renault F1 Team
